Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(942,362)}白水母记
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位聆听多比迪克的惊险传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the terrific, tumultuous tale of Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我鱼实玛利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Call me Fishmael
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我年轻时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my youth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾是一位青春无畏的出道学徒工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was an intrepid, fresh-faced journeyman
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.36,0:01:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行进在各个城市间  寻找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,looking from town to town for any work I could find
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.31,0:01:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时我并不知道  我将要踏上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little did I know, I was about to step in some
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish jelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,430)}大水母客店
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临大水母客店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Jelly Squirt Inn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can we help, me hearty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要喝水母汁  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have some jelly juice, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm job hunting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢问你们有没有什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Might you lubbers have employment
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让拥有收银经验的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for an able-legged young buck
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双腿健全年轻人负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with cash register experience?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我才能碰我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody touches me money but me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么买水母酱  要么滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy some jelly, or get out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.71,0:02:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard tell
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有艘叫老菠萝的船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that a boat called "Ye Olde Pineapple"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上要出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is shipping out soon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要多招水手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they need more hands
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你手就挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got plenty of hands
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像听到他们切船的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I hear them cutting the ship right now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  不过我晕船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I always get seasick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会上船的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be caught dead on a ship
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种话让我倍感遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to hear that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Egads
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被绑架了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been squid-napped
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.35,0:03:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.19,0:03:19.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长有份特别的工作要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:19.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The captain has a special job just for ye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, for ye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实挺需要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I do need a job
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正晕船就晕船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I get seasick, I get seasick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来让你熟悉门道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show ye the ropes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1160,920)}绳 子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有大绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the big rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the little rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦瓜脸绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the frowny rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑脸绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the smiley rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有甘草绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the licorice rope
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会打结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to tie a knot?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会  不过我愿意学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, but I'd love to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll teach ya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}之后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast ye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵亚哈船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I be Captain Sponge-Hab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带你们来  是要执行特别任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought you all here for a special mission--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猎捕巨大白水母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to hunt down the great white jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克就是那只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was Dopey Dick the beast
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夺去你的腿的野兽吗  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who took off thy leg, Captain?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Naw
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿都挤进锅铲柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg is all squeezed into the handle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是爱听我锅铲碰地的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love the sound my spatula makes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克是一只巨大白水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick is a great white jellyfish, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大小有如一间分层套房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he's the size of a split-level condominium
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好好寻找多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So keep your eyes peeled for Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果找到了就大声通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if ye spot him, just give me a holler
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到的话就应该是这种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what you should do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you actually see him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母就是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish be dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,追上那座雪山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chase that snow-hilled hump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  戴着漂亮羊毛帽的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, in the smart wool cap
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有份特殊活儿要让你干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a special job for ye
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I be ready
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是特殊活儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the special job?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来当黏性鱼叉枪刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll make a great sticky harpoon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  我现在要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now I'm gonna throw up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢一点吧  多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please slow down, Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没什么好吐的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything left to throw up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我知道怎么抚慰凶猛的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know how to soothe a savage beast
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.85,0:07:49.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我耳朵在咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:49.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ears are biting me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克抵抗不了音乐的吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick cannot resist the music
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家动作快  收绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, everyone, reel him in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  各位兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, me hearties
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.55,0:08:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来到了猎捕水母最好的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,comes the best part of hunting down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and catching a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.57,0:08:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抹水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spreading the jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you sillies
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要放了水母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Releasing the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞离这里吧  多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly and be free, Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, mateys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice catch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该你们放了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to release him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才不会放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not releasing bupkis
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕我们要留着多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we're just gonna keep Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖它的水母酱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sell his jelly for money
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么能肆意压榨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can he exploit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如此稀有又温驯的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,such a rare and gentle creature?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克是我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick is our friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们以为能乘虚而入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if ye think you're just gonna swoop in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我们朋友关进笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and put our friend in a cage
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们麻烦就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ye've got another thing coming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  忠诚船员们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, me loyal crew?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiver me timbers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个反向叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a reverse mutiny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fake-Beard
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.95,0:09:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带这个上甲板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put this in your poop deck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是哑炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ye cannonball is a dud
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.97,0:10:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.67,0:10:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须从那群海盗手里救回多比迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to save Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from them pilfering pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要更大的菠萝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need a bigger pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scupper that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派巴克  跟上那群舱底的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-Buck, follow those bilge rats
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  海绵亚哈船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Captain Sponge-Hab
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肚子安静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet, stomach
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会吵醒大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll wake everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me, me hearties
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你啊  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.25,0:12:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:06.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1694,718)}水母酱
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐好了  多比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sit tight, Dopey
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会帮你解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna cut you loose
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再电下去就救不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if he keeps doing that, we won't
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了  多比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All free, Dopey
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母多美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't jellyfishing wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.11,0:12:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人欠了我三百吨水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody owes me 300 tons of jellyfish jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道章鱼有没有酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if octopuses give jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do they?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好心人  你收欠条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kind sir, will ye take an IOU?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要扒下你的一只眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take an eye
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者两只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do ye hear it, lads?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.87,0:13:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey Dick's song
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还有机会能捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance to catch him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人进入战斗岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, beat to quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃鱼叉枪吧  傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hardy har-poon, sucker
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dopey, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我解开  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut me loose, you Dopey dunce
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了心头的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For hate's sake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要和你拼到最后一息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we spit our last breath at thee
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵亚哈船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Sponge-Hab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不想在这工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna work here anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是我成为了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's how I became
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.34,0:14:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多比迪克猎捕过程中唯一的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the sole survivor of the hunt for Dopey Dick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才不是唯一的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You weren't the sole survivor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were all there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my story
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the hero
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.27,0:14:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想怎么结局就怎么结局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can end it any way I want
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼实玛利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fishmael
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.70,0:15:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家再请一份水母汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all buying another round of jelly juice
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群得坏血病的猪头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those scurvy swine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是不懂什么故事才算好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wouldn't know a good story
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡吃点苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it bit them on the--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.49,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs165\fsp50\c&H00FF91&}痞老板与魔豆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(695.802,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(715.802,660)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:34.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(759.802,668)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(631.802,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,550)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.95,0:15:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一只幼稚的小浮游生物  名叫杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there lived a naive little plankton named Jack
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杰克的海霸农场干枯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jack's Chum Farm had dried up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且身上还只剩一法寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he only had one single farthing left
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.02,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 法寻：货币单位，4法寻合1便士 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去市场买食物的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to buy food at the market
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fear not, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钟表老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my clockwork wife
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会好好花这最后一法寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will spend our last farthing wisely
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让咱俩免受饥饿之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save us from starvation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,322)}马上发财\N魔豆只要一法寻
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上发财
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get rich now?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic bean?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要一法寻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only one farthing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ka-ching
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hit the jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感恩海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank King Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赚到食物和清漆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you get plenty of food and varnish?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比那强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better than that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有魔豆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a magical bean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.91,0:16:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么处理  煮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you do, boil it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是用来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's magic
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杰克啊  你居然用咱最后一点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jack, I can't believe you blew our last penny
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费在一颗破豆子上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a stupid bean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我还需要清漆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still need varnish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我不会让你挨饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm not gonna let you go hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open wide
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说魔豆不是用来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, you don't eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm full
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you so, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he goes--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了吵赢无所不用其极
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anything to win an argument
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会强健心脏我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care if they are good for my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我再也不吃豆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am never eating another bean
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:41.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,328)}老蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Ye Old Krusty Krab"?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许里面有人可以帮我发大财
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone there can make me rich
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有人快噎死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone is choking to death
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鹅跑过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Galloping goose flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是出于好意  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I meant well, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看准了再啄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're pecking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个鸟毛怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you foul-feathered freak
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.90,0:18:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闻到了地上凡人的血味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell the blood of a Bottomite
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是你  海绵大鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just you, SpongeGoose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再喂你吃凡人食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to stop feeding you people food
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大鹅乖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be a good goose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我下点蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and lay some Krabby Patties on me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法竖琴  奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic harp, do your thing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.14,0:19:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好难听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以吃的金子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Edible gold
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rich
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  魔豆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, magic bean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就要开吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁胆敢侵犯我的一方净土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who disturbs me inner sanctum?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天天气好差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crazy weather, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got ya
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你到底有没有被关着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whether you're caged or whether you're loose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都得给我去喂我黄金大鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll feed you to me golden goose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  别让我喂鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not the goose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能有黄金小不点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have a solid gold pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概要四个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in about four hours
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peekaboo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点跑  跑过来的大鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giddy up, galloping goose flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弃鹅逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abandon goose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了鹅会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot geese can fly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  不讲童话故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, enough of this storybook stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来打激光枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's laser time, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Timber
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  大鹅你留着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can keep the goose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.78,0:21:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杰克  看你对我们家干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jack, look what you did to our house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚为你灭了个巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just slayed a giant for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能别批我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to lay off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:49.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,726)}之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242,618)}黄金堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,232)}快来看魔鹅跳舞
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.53,0:22:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔豆确实有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That bean was magic
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你在这神奇的一天要买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what can I get for you on this magical day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my good sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来一份双层黄金堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like a double gold patty combo, please
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不穿衣服不穿鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No shirt, no shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身上没壳  不提供服务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no shell, no service
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚吧  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a hike, tiny
